13
00:01:04,010 --> 00:01:07,400
Baby points and says, &quot;moon,&quot; everybody enjoys that.

14
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:12,040
It seems like she knows what moon refers to, but then you bring her inside and when she

15
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:15,190
