16
00:01:15,190 --> 00:01:18,490
When she sees the light bulb turns on, she goes, &quot;moon.&quot;

17
00:01:18,490 --> 00:01:22,400
When she sees a circle drawn on a piece of paper, she says, &quot;moon&quot;.

18
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:27,690
Now, this is interesting because the baby hasn&#39;t had an opportunity in social context

19
00:01:27,690 --> 00:01:31,500
