20
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:33,640
She goes and does it on her own.

21
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:36,890
It&#39;s called an overextension error.

22
00:01:36,890 --> 00:01:40,500
Just about all babies do overextensions.

23
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:44,480
Far fewer babies make underextension errors (Reich 1976).

24
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:48,300
